        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Hydrogen Permitting Simplification Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill exempts certain major federal actions, including actions that produce hydrogen from nuclear, solar, wind, or geothermal energy sources, from requirements under the National Environmental Policy Act of 1969.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
